{"tid":2462652,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"打針後感到「好精神」「打左好過唔打 就算死或生，都唔好累街坊」長者：諗住會返內地玩吓","createTime":"2021-03-26T06:38:04.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-26T06:44:51.000Z","uid":230530,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"0411ef303d06d8fc874f67d67e8101648b9bfc98","tid":2462652,"uid":230530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T06:38:04.000Z","msg":"今早陸續有市民到官涌體育館分別打第一針和第二針，惟未見如初期排隊至門外的情況，整個早上只有約150人到場接種疫苗。<br />\n<br />\n「諗住會返內地玩吓。」打過第二針的王太在步出接種中心時表現淡定，她表示希望完成兩次接種，讓自己在通關後能盡快到內地遊玩。政府專家曾指出接種第二針的免疫反應會較第一針大，但王太未有特別擔心，「唔會嘅，多啲休息囉」，更指對科興疫苗「有信心」。<br />\n<br />\n屬60歲以上優先接種群組的楊先生表示，未有因連串的嚴重事故考慮停打或轉針，更指打過第二針感到「好精神」，認為接種疫苗可保護其他市民，「打咗好過唔打，就算死或生，都唔好累街坊。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20210326/FFG24F3Y6RERDBFXQUEUFSZTMQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20210326%2FFFG24F3Y6RERDBFXQUEUFSZTMQ%2F&d=eMoIgPJs71q5KSiTXOS1GicuUNiPSPuqsSoNSJcc%2FI4%3D&h=59404c9c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20210326%2FFFG24F3Y6RERDBFXQUEUFSZTMQ%2F&h=d829010f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20210326/FFG24F3Y6RERDBFXQUEUFSZTMQ/</a>"},{"pid":"eb137dc915053784976b17e6c16d74b929f0d063","tid":2462652,"uid":230530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T06:39:58.000Z","msg":"嚴先生指接種第二劑科興疫苗後未有特別感覺，「完全冇嘢...（與第一針相比）完全冇分別。」他表示，每日都會有市民因不同的疾病而不適，認為報道指因接種疫苗所致是「誤導」。"},{"pid":"affa680ba86783fcedba60c4979b92d24d6a3218","tid":2462652,"uid":242537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T06:43:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmSMyMvGjD2TDEBVDWHmBCwXQaZj1TYKGiCwFqsDDDwkxS?filename=PiwxpvN.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPiwxpvN.gif&h=cfd51a6e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3d2d5ba162ddb6e7f1b35ad550b24e15e07781d6","tid":2462652,"uid":59920,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T06:44:51.000Z","msg":"記者有冇抄低聯絡方法<br />\n七日後再搵佢做訪問<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}